{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":147475,"duration_api_ms":147076,"num_turns":7,"result":"**Verdict: APPROVED_WITH_NOTES**\n\nThe Milestone 5 implementation is solid. Shell quality is clean — `bash -n` and `shellcheck` both pass with zero warnings. Architecture boundaries respected (only `lib/plan.sh` modified, 251 lines, well under the 300-line limit). The four-action review loop (`y/e/r/n`) is correctly implemented with `/dev/tty` input handling and `TEKHTON_TEST_MODE` bypass matching the established pattern.\n\nThree non-blocking notes:\n1. **Misleading \"Files written\" message** — `[y]` prints a success message implying it writes files, but the files were already written by Step 4 (generation agent). The message should say \"files are ready\" rather than \"files written.\"\n2. **Editor non-zero exit** — if the editor aborts with a non-zero exit code, `set -euo pipefail` will silently kill the function. A `|| true` guard would make this more robust.\n3. **Double file read** — `_display_milestone_summary()` opens CLAUDE.md twice (once for project name, once for milestones). Minor inefficiency, not a correctness issue.\n\nNo blockers. Ready to advance.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"dd110872-be97-4008-b982-b8c54a6bd0b2","total_cost_usd":0.2465424,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":25700,"cache_read_input_tokens":148778,"output_tokens":7034,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":25700,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":8,"outputTokens":7034,"cacheReadInputTokens":148778,"cacheCreationInputTokens":25700,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.2465424,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"fba7332c-c970-47f9-ae6c-2ec627cfe0da"}
